lenders.name: Stilfol
lenders.occupational_info:
Mit Stilfol kann man in nur wenigen Schritten seine eigene selbstklebende Folie machen. Einfach ein Foto hochladen oder aus über 7 Millionen Vorlagen ein Motiv aussuchen. Maße können selbst bestimmt werden. Wer keine selbstklebende Folie will, kann sich auch die Folie als Poster zukommen lassen.

Die Folien können an fast alles angebracht werden, was eine glatte pberfläche hat. Vom Tisch bis zum Auto ist da alle möglich. Das anbringen und auch das Abziehen der Folien ist ganz einfach und hinterlässt keine Supren.

lenders.name: Yvette
lenders.loan_because:
I've been researching my family history for over 20 years. I've seen what the impact of a small event can be in the course of history. Ancestors who were the only ones to survive out of 10 siblings. Ancestors who were brave enough to move to start a better life and wouldn't have met their spouses otherwise. Without these events, I wouldn't be here today. 

I'd like to think that just maybe, my donation will make a difference in somebody's life today and in the lives of their descendants for generations to come. Sometimes all you need is a chance.
lenders.occupational_info:
I work as a professional genealogist, helping people from around the world find their ancestors from the Netherlands. I've recently started making a Kiva loan for each new client I get.  

I also work as a project manager at the Nationaal Archief, the National Archives of the Netherlands. My professional interests include online access to historical information and improving accessibility of websites for people with disabilities.
